# 📊 MSC-CGI vs BSC-CGI Alignment Analysis (Power Query)

## 🧩 Overview

This project focuses on validating and comparing **MSC-CGI** and **BSC-CGI** datasets to ensure consistency and alignment across telecom network nodes.

Using Power Query within Microsoft Excel / Power BI, the pipeline ingests raw 3G network data, transforms it into standardized formats, and produces a consolidated comparison output to identify mismatches, gaps, or inconsistencies between MSC and BSC configurations.

